Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好  我笔丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I lost my pen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以借我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can borrow mine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.77,0:01:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我曾经也丢过一次东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost something once
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.18,0:01:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我丢过一辈子离不开的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost something I couldn't live without
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My identity
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之  谢谢你借我笔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So anyway, thanks for the pen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, hon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.51,0:01:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都要从上周说起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It all started last week
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准确来说是上周一早上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monday morning to be exact
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正是在那天丢失了身份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The day I lost my identity
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.55,0:01:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, world
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.71,0:01:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有住在世界里的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all who inhabit it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.28,0:01:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, help
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.06,0:01:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.97,0:01:53.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:53.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174,904)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, are you there?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.27,0:01:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:01:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.21,0:02:00.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:00.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你来当我眼睛  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you to be my eyes, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我离卫生间近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I near the bathroom?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.81,0:02:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.97,0:02:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gar?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我这场可怕事件结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that my horrific incident of terror is over
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来吃早餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how 'bout some breakfast?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天当中最重要的一餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The most important meal of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,端出小蜗一贯的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Serving it up Gary's way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878,894)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请慢用  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喂小蜗这么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I've been feeding this to Gary for years
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连蜗牛粮什么味道都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I don't even know what it tastes like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1054,944)}蜗牛粮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,902)}蜗牛粮\N世界总部
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.75,0:02:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  彼得森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Peterson?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不太确定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.02,0:02:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点不适
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a disturbance
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那是我吃过最难吃的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the worst thing I've ever tasted
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  至少再也不会吃这玩意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, at least I'll never have to do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那一堆把戏害我上班快迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All these shenanigans made me late for work
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身份到底什么时候丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When exactly did you lose your identity?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  谁又是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and who's Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么要吃蜗牛粮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you eat Snail-Po?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耐心一点  两位善人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patience, good people
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好故事的节奏可不能赶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A great story can't be rushed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我要直接跳到蟹堡王那段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,However, I will skip ahead to The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.56,0:03:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以我炽热的真心温热烤制而成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,grilled with the fiery warmth of my beating heart
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真应该戴一个身份牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you really should be wearing a name tag
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方便我好好感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can thank you properly
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然与客人产生分歧有违我的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While it is against my philosophy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to disagree with a customer
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我必须指出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must point out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我其实戴着一个身份牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I am, in fact, wearing a name tag
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.96,0:04:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward, it's terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最可怕的事就这样发生在我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the most terrible thing that's ever happened to me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身份牌弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my name tag
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pourquoi?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, take it easy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以再弄一个新的身份牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can get a new one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不要新身份牌  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't want a new one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的身份牌肯定就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name tag is out there somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lost
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又挨饿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁会伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who will help it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一被谁用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if someone's using it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(894,182)}银行
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.98,0:04:40.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:40.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, nobody move
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:45.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(544,786)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是银行抢劫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a bank robbery
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿提卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attica
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.07,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 本台词改自电影《热天午后》相关情节\N指1971年阿提卡监狱暴动事件 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  我是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm innocent, I tell ya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:58.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(774,704)}奢华生活\N文摘
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fainted
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你刚弄丢了身份牌什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you lost your name tag or something
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你能不能镇静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, will you get ahold of yourself?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么时候把身份牌弄丢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since when is losing your name tag
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得连天都要塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the end of the world?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体员工请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, all employees
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稍微提醒一下  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a quick heads-up, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.42,0:05:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一小时后有仪容仪表突击检查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,uniform inspection in one hour
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡检查没通过的都会被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone who doesn't pass, gets the boot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1044,920)}得 到 靴 子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而这个靴子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This boot, to be exact
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常臭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's very stinky
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要穿一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you have to wear it all day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一小时后见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you in an hour
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  如果你真想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, if you really want
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你的身份牌  就重走来时路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to find your name tag, just retrace your steps
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重走来时路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Retrace my steps?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A genius
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道  不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know about that, but
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你帮我代班  我等会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cover me till I get back, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.18,0:05:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A genius
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.82,0:05:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不然就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how about
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想重走来时路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to retrace my steps
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须回忆今早做过的所有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to remember everything I did this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.84,0:05:58.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:58.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今早向我说过嗨  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said hi to me this morning, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我每早都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As I do every morning
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I need you to do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.72,0:06:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可没这个义务  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't part of the deal, Squarepants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的问候可不是什么录音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hellos aren't just some tape recording
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又不能供你倒带  一遍遍重放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you can rewind and play over and over
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是特别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're special
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这可是紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, this is an emergency
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今早丢了身份牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my name tag this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得重走来时路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I need to retrace my steps
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你丢了身份牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lost your name tag?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你应该知道计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, you know the plan, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要重走来时路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to retrace your steps
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到你路过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when you walk by me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就会像今早那样说嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say, "Hi," just like this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来得直接重走到醒来的那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I should start with when I woke up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿会有用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure hope this works
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, world
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有住在世界里的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all who inhabit it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目前为止还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So far, so good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没在上面看到我身份牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see my name tag up here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我这场可怕事件结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that my horrific incident of terror is over
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来吃早餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how 'bout some breakfast?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天当中最重要的一餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The most important meal of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.83,0:07:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,端出小蜗一贯的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Serving it up Gary's way
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来就只要走出门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next I just have to walk outside
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟派大星说嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and say hi to Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要跟我说声嗨的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to say hi to me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  从头再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, let's take it from the top
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回可别忘了念你台词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your line this time
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, world
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有住在世界里的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all who inhabit it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天当中最重要的一餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The most important meal of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's way
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  怎么不跟我说嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, why didn't you say hi to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我动力是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's my motivation?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管动力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the motivation
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.96,0:07:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说嗨就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just say hi
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.99,0:08:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try it again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵卜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBoob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵卜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBoob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I said
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是海绵卜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's SpongeBoob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说了海绵卜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said SpongeBoob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again, again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, people
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天当中最重要的一餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The most important meal of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.35,0:08:31.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我笑场了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:31.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the giggles
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the use?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下没法及时找到身份牌应对检查了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never find my name tag in time for inspection
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今早跟你说嗨后  你做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what did you do after I said hi to you this morning?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.90,0:08:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我高高兴兴跳去了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I skipped merrily to The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟老头简金斯问好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Said hello to old man Jenkins
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  老简
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. J
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往蟹老板桌上放了个苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Placed an apple on Mr. Krabs's desk
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that's about it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有俩人把我丢垃圾箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And these two guys threw me in the dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身份牌就在蟹老板桌上的苹果里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your name tag is in the apple on Mr. Krabs' desk
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  苹果现在可能被扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, he's probably thrown it away by now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就到垃圾箱里面找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then, we'll look in the dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么臭味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that stench?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是发现之味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is the stench of discovery
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.12,0:09:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.96,0:09:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我推你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a boost
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hop on, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,习惯之后就没那么臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad, once you get used to it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我长了鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a nose
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾的温度刚刚好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the garbage is fine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炮弹来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannonball
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那边找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look over there
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll look over here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在找了  在找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm looking, I'm looking
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽快在找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm looking as fast as I can
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, let me get that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.05,0:10:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有张刺魟5000的单曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Stingray 5000 single
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这伙人可酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These guys rock
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会有谁想把这种宝贝丢掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would anybody throw this away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,458)}刺魟{\fnArial}5000
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.01,0:10:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是忘了我们在找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten what we're looking for
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么还沉迷在昨日前40金曲中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knee deep in yesterday's Top 40 songs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你个提示  两个词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a hint: Two words
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一个词  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First word, "my"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二个词  身份牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Second word, "name tag"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能再来个提示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I have another hint?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我很想傻坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I would love to sit here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪你玩问答游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and play "20 Questions" with you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是离检查就只差一分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I've only got one minute till inspection
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一分钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One minute?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536,846)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在没空  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not now, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你身份牌在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know where your name tag is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.29,0:10:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.72,0:10:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't remember
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我没空陪你这么闹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I don't have time for this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你到底在挺我还是损我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, are you with me or against me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, could you give me a hint?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.39,0:11:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大喊身份牌的小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boy who cried, "Name tag"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你不打算帮我忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦你爬回你石头底下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then just go crawl back under your rock
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我自己不会穿反衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I don't wear my shirt backwards
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.39,0:11:13.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿反衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:13.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My shirt backward?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我衣服穿反了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My shirt's on backwards
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我的身份一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had my identity all along
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.79,0:11:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体集合  准备检查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fall in for inspection
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帽子和制服看着很整洁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hat and uniform seem to be in order
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向我保证今晚会刮鼻子  你就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Promise me you'll shave tonight and you pass
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoo-rah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boy, your turn
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证你会发现一切整洁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find everything ship-shape
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的水母啊  什么臭味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumping jellyfish, what's that stench?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.72,0:11:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发现之味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Discovery?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是  我找回了我的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's how I got my identity back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的故事讲完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, that's my story
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你正好打发了11分钟时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you managed to kill 11 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(872,268)}需要服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(884,764)}贝蒂
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贝蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Betty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.38,0:12:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又不是贝蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweetie, I'm not Betty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是借了她的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just borrowed her uniform
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己的制服拿去干洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while mine's at the cleaners
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.72,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,229)}痞老板的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(335.802,504)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:27.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(377.802,584)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.67\pos(379.802,294)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(335.802,408)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(519.802,706)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:37.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,466)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内有美味的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,home of the delicious Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及蟹堡王的超机密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and its super-secret recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请注意  蟹堡王的员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Krusty Krab crew
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体成员立刻报到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hands report immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎炸厨师海绵宝宝报到  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fry Cook SpongeBob reporting, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底在喊什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all the yelling about?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天可是25周年纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today is the 25th anniversary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.82,0:12:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纪念我的死对头痞老板第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the first time me archenemy Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前来偷我的蟹黄堡秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever tried to steal me secret Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方能给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have the secret formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.10,0:12:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他坚持不懈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he was persistent
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他用过伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He used disguise
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超科学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Super-science
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,184)}我不是蟑螂
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非暴力反抗运动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,civil disobedience
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我总是占得上风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I always came out on top
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太迷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fascinating
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他失败了那么多次  变得诡计多端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But thousands of failures have made him crafty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以务必严加提防
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so keep your eyes open
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们永远不知道他会用什么诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never know what trick he'll use
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来偷取我的蟹黄堡秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to steal me secret Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个古雅的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a quaint restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要采样他们的货品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I will sample their wares
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How weird
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做成顾客模样的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A machine made to look like a customer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你去冲一下男厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, why don't you go hose out the men's room
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With pleasure, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来应付这位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take this one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.58,0:13:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡王  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to The Krusty Krab, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要点一份辣珊瑚块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like an order of chili coral bits
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定不要蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't want a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这点够付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will this cover it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.25,0:14:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.31,0:14:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这肯定是痞老板的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was sure it was one of Plankton's tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码他的钱能用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least his money's good
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你明知道我永不怀疑金钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You knew I would never distrust a dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上给我交出蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, hand over the secret Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or what?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都没想过会走到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd get this far
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我来指点你下一步怎么走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then, allow me to suggest your next move
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来喝点带劲儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for the chaser
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:59.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1098,506)}裤头村市
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just wait, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次我会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time I'll
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在逗谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:03.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,582)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.30,0:15:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码回家还有通情达理的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I can go home to a wife who understands
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  说说看怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, tell me what happened
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完全不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来就踏实多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talking will make you feel better
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是这种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's your problem
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事都憋在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never let anyone in
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你非要当顽石  非要当独行侠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton the rock, Plankton the loner
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她又来了  女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And she's off, ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.69,0:15:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你非要亲力亲为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to do everything yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.66,0:15:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你不管做什么都是这个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why everything you try ends up like this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And like this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近是这个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And more recently, like this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没那么废
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not that bad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.76,0:15:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只是需要一点帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just require a little help
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然找点打手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe some henchmen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Henchmen?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you need to do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.41,0:15:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在身边多招一点雄壮肌肉男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is surround yourself with muscular tough guys
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他们听你指挥就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who will do whatever you say
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么说还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like the sound of that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.65,0:16:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就到全镇所有肮脏文盲小会所游说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:16:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll canvass all the seediest lowbrow dives in town
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寻找我的小喽啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to find my minions
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好会说他们的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I know just how to speak their language
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝贺大家  各位犯罪分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Felicitations, malefactors
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正在拼尽全力盗取
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am endeavoring to misappropriate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.99,0:16:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,廉价食品所需的配方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the formulary for the preparation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of affordable comestibles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想跟我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who will join me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter what I do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.21,0:16:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后的下场都是被比我大的人踩扁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always end up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,being squashed by someone bigger than me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你多半是过激了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're overreacting
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.22,0:16:33.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:33.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟海底其他数百万浮游生物没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm no different than the millions of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,other plankton in the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,692)}左腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,692)}右腿
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮游生物家族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The plankton family
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长久以来受人摆布  又任人践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has always been pushed around and stepped on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然单打独斗确实力量微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Acting alone, we're powerless
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但只要联合起来  浮游生物家族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but united, the plankton family
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会是眼中钉肉中刺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could be a real pain in the belly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,460)}电话簿
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹多半以为一只浮游生物好对付
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs may think one plankton is no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,280)}浮游生物
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要来看看他能不能对付两只
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but let's see him take on two
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者十只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or ten
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者一百只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or 100
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者一千只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or 1,000
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,何止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why stop there?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.49,0:17:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要召集天涯海角所有家族成员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll gather every family member
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from every corner of the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1102,292)}亲爱的浮游生物\N你好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让整个浮游生物家族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The entire plankton family
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,聚在同一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,under one roof
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,140)}呼叫全体浮游生物
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹绝对没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs won't stand a chance
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敌得过我这一大队智囊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,against the staggering intellect
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.22,0:17:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多达百万的高智商犯罪智多星大军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of a million super-smart criminal masterminds
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, brethren
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look here, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是痞老表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Cousin Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我离家久得连我都记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been away from home longer than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  老表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, howdy, cousin
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  克莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, Clem
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然  你肯定记得齐克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, you remember Zeke
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.88,0:17:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲁弗斯  吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rufus, Jete
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比利鲍勃  比利吉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Billy Bob, Billy Jim
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比利比利波维利巴那那法那佛菲利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Billy Billy Bo Willy Banana Fana Fo Filly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,道格  伊那斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doug, Enos
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朱利欧  弗莱彻麦基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Julio, Fletcher McGee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雷恩柴尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rainchild
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进  大家别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come inside, make yourself at home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给大家认识一下我的电脑老婆凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to meet my computer wife, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Golly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她可真漂亮  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she sure is pretty, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我真名就叫那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's my first name
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you please?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.35,0:18:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚说到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as I was saying
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.19,0:18:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  谢尔顿这名字确实很好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, we all know Sheldon's a funny name
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,O-ho-kay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  笑完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm done
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.36,0:18:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会再笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.35,0:18:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To continue
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有你们能将荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only you can bring honor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1164,666)}谢尔顿
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1186,438)}谢尔顿
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.80,0:18:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带回浮游生物家族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to the plankton
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718,232)}谢尔顿
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多年以来  我的目标就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For years, it has been my goal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(798,240)}谢尔顿
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得到秘方  当作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to acquire the secret formula for
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.84,0:18:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:18:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bottom line
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们入侵蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we invade The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我偷到秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can steal the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.26,0:19:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对我们有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in it for us?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about us?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我班卓琴换根新弦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I get a new string for my banjo?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能找到跟这只相配的靴子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And another boot to match this 'un?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我笔记本电脑加点内存吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And some more memory for my laptop?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有根啤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about root beer?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根啤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Root beer?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我把秘方弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me get the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.84,0:19:28.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想喝多少根啤就有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:28.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you can have as much root beer as you can drink
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我痞老板要来取胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Victory, thy name is plankton
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,926)}谢尔顿
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快要关门了  连续好几小时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's almost closing time, and we haven't seen
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.58,0:19:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都没看到痞老板的眼睛或者触须
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eye or antenna of old Plankton for hours
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  想必他这次总算是放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, I think this time, he's finally given up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意了  蟹堡王的经营者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Krusty Krab management
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你们的上级
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your better speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经把这家餐厅包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have the restaurant surrounded
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把秘密配方给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.36,0:20:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就毁掉蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:20:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll destroy The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你一个能拿我怎么样  臭虫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and what army, bug?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就我一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What army?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就我一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What army?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你四周  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look around you, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你种了草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You planted grass?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,草
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grass?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对不会得逞的  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never get away with it, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水管太窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the pipes are much too narrow
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.04,0:20:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况我真正想要的是蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, what I really want is the Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you might as well forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方就锁在我保险柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The formula is locked away in me safe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会告诉你密码多少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll never give you the combination
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.32,0:20:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们完全有能力自己解开密码吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're more than capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,figuring it out for ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boys?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.96,0:21:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往左一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little to the left
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse you plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你们合体变成人耳的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your ability to join together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to form a working human ear
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dog
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The formula's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.81,0:21:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过了这么多年  总算是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all these years, it's finally mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要昭告天下  今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let it be known that on this day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,248)}蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.85,0:21:35.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  谢尔顿痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:35.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, Sheldon J Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.16,0:21:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单枪匹马推翻了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,single-handedly overthrew The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.04,0:21:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然  还得到了家族的一点帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-And of course, I had a little help from the family
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不能看秘方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't look at the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求情没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Begging won't help
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.65,0:21:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  你可绝对受不住真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, you won't be able to handle the truth
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.68,0:21:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上有些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's some things in this world
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一般人的双眼看不得的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that weren't meant for mortal eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.70,0:22:00.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:00.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eye
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.94,0:22:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eye
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击鼓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drumroll, please
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于  过了这么多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, after all these years
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.38,0:22:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算能查明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm about to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:15.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,214)}蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.78,0:22:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,究竟是什么能让蟹黄堡这么好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what makes a Krabby Patty taste so good
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.02,0:22:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的秘密配方就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The secret recipe for one Krabby Patty is
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.42,0:22:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一小撮盐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"A pinch of salt"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三茶匙洋葱碎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"three teaspoons of chopped onions"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.23,0:22:26.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:26.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.16,0:22:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一杯爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"a cup of love"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.62,0:22:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.75,0:22:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,混合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"mixed together
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.85,0:22:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后再加上最重要的原料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"with the most important ingredient of all
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.38,0:22:37.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四磅成堆的现磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:37.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"four heaping pounds of freshly ground
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,plankton"?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.45,0:22:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都警告过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I warned you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.02,0:22:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:22:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why ain't you running?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.37,0:23:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不识字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't read
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.67,0:23:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.17,0:23:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错过什么了没
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I miss anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.07,0:23:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  这真是蟹黄堡的秘密原料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:11.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, is this really
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the secret ingredient for the Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.28,0:23:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.00,0:23:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板多半会发现被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Plankton'll probably figure that out
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.93,0:23:20.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上回来找真正的秘方是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:20.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and be back again to find out what the real formula is
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过放心好了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.29,0:23:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方安全得很
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The formula's safe from harm
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.50,0:23:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把它藏到我最隐秘的藏身处了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it hidden in me most secret hiding place
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.24,0:23:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人  就连痞老板都想不到这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A place no one, not even Plankton, would ever figure out
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.75,0:23:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.78,0:23:36.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就放在你家床垫底下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:36.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's at home under your mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.74,0:23:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Squidward
